{"tid":120647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：中國政府在香港特首產生過程中有權力","createTime":"2017-02-14T14:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T00:48:24.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bab863afc8fd0799fd2281fbf5a90ca0727e6c3f","tid":120647,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T14:48:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/02/cy-leung-14/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2017%2F02%2Fcy-leung-14%2F&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=631663a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2017/02/cy-leung-14/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/0214_cy-leung.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F0214_cy-leung.jpg&h=79a47c68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首梁振英今日（十四日）表示，不論在政改問題或特首選舉問題上，根據《基本法》中國政府在香港有它的權力，在行使權力時，亦履行中國政府對全國、對香港的責任。他說，中國政府在行政長官整個產生過程中有的權力，並指任何一個特首參選人或候選人都不能隨便排除中國政府對香港的權力。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英指，中國政府對香港政改，它有的權力、八三一方案它的權力根源，以至中國政府在行政長官整個產生過程中有的權力，它對全國的責任，都是嚴肅的事情，要認真、要認識清楚。"},{"pid":"4bebab65fc865d451b7e689afde21c6da92a46f4","tid":120647,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"又係語言偽術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國政府係特首產生既過程係有權力啊, <br />\n不過<span style=\"color: red;\">正常黎講</span>中國唯一既權力就係任命特首, 而唔係推條友出黎迫你班人選佢"},{"pid":"bc38d6d5e9e15fdb779b0af0ccb9ca76fd5d3ca4","tid":120647,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"選特首, 係關國防定外交事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb88a6086e79852cdf8a238c74fa497bb9ab42f5","tid":120647,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>選特首, 係關國防定外交事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外交<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958b8bee64ffd8e1c8d1a08999bb43357ff9078f","tid":120647,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"你都個頭近啦仲咁多口水"},{"pid":"40828126dbb9ecba07f7df50d2f532d699541ddd","tid":120647,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"知啦，知共匪有權力DQ你條柒頭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15558c42142caf1e7c25a0b28c19db632bb90a12","tid":120647,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T00:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}